{
  "stem": "717.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Maybe a foot away from the-- from the the steel refinery, they built bricks around it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "This was our job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And then we also built-- there was one job that was called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "We called-- we built a bunker for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "I think it was a 35-foot ceiling poured with concrete.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "I remember I was running with the-- with a wheelbarrow full with mixed concrete, on a board maybe that wide, running, that was slippery from the snow.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "You'd be surprised the things you can do when you got a guy with a rifle behind you, and the rifle's pointed at you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "You can perform miracles which otherwise you couldn't do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "This camp had about 800 to 1,000 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "When we came, there were already some people there from Hungary-- there were some Hungarian Jews-- and some from Kielce, from a city called Kielce.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "It's a big city in Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "We were the last group that they brought there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "The Kommandant of this camp was a Pole, a German Pole.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "Before the war, he was an officer in the Polish Calvary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "Now he was an SS man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "His name was Kovel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "In fact, I met people here that were under him in a different camp, and they knew what a brutal monster that was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "He managed, in a small camp like that, to have his private crematorium to burn the people that died-- no, over there they didn't have a gas chamber-- so that he doesn't have to transport them or bury them.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "His own crematorium, he had, for one person.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked there, that was in August.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I worked there until January, '45.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was very scared.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know why I used to get slapped every day.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
